  Basque Headlines Topic Classification (BHTC) dataset

 Version: 2.0
 Last update: (2021/11/09)
 Changes from 1.0 version:
    - v1.0 had texts in lower cased and punctuations removed. Now original texts are provided.
    - Deleted some duplicates and examples not in Basque from train.
    


The corpus  contains 12,296 news  headlines  (brief  article  descriptions) from  the  Basque  weekly  newspaper  Argia (https://www.argia.eus). News are classified uniquely according to twelve thematic categories.  The dataset was divided into train (70%), development (15%) and test datasets (15%).



Dataset format
----------------

 The dataset is divided in three files:
     - train.jsonl (8585 examples)
     - val.jsonl (1857 examples)
     - test.jsonl (1854 examples)
     
 Each row is a headline. The rows have the following data: label(topic) & text

 Possible topic categories for label are stored in the following ones:
[Ekonomia, Euskal_Herria, Euskara, Gizartea, Historia, Ingurumena, Iritzia, Komunikazioa, Kultura, Nazioartea, Politika, Zientzia]



